            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "; it was about a mile from Bethlehem to the south (i), and is supposed to be the place where the shepherds were watching their flocks, when the angel reported to them the birth of Christ, ",
            "children": []
